                    <h4 class="head-lg text-red fw-400" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">01</h4>
                    <h3 class="head-sm fw-400" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Regular meetings with the community</h3>
                    <p class="text-md mt-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">On Dec 1st, 2021, Phoenix Copper held its first open meeting, at which we directly addressed questions and concerns from over 130 of our neighbors and wider stakeholders. These meetings will be held on a regular basis.</p>
                    <p class="text-md mt-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">CEO Ryan McDermott’s presentation can be downloaded here. Information arising from the Q&A can be downloaded in summary form here.</p>
                </div>
