                    <h3 class="head-sm fw-400" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Konnex Community Committee</h3>
                    <p class="text-md mt-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">The Konnex Community Committee will be made up of Mackay citizens to foster a spirit of transparency and open communication and to provide a platform for the exchange of information and expertise.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container communities">
        <div class="row flex-center">
