            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="community-content">
                    <h4 class="head-lg text-red fw-400" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">03</h4>
                    <h3 class="head-sm fw-400" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">The Konnex Good Neighbor Agreement</h3>
                    <p class="text-md mt-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
                        This is currently being drafted, and is based on similar agreements which have operated successfully between mining
                        companies and the communities in which they operate elsewhere.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container communities">
        <div class="row flex-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img class="img-fluid w-100" src="images/education-img.jpg" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="community-content">
                    <h4 class="head-lg text-red fw-400" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">04</h4>
                    <h3 class="head-sm fw-400" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Education</h3>
                    <p class="text-md mt-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">The greater the number of students in the local school, the more revenue will be channelled to the school, allowing them to spend more on learning resources and extra-curricular activities.</p>
                    <p class="text-md mt-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Our geologists currently work with the local high school’s FFA program (Future Farmers of America) to foster interest in mining activities and to inspire enthusiasm for the industry in the future.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


